com.cyc.baseclient.util

Class ResultSetSlice

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cyc.baseclient.util.ResultSetSlice

  • public class ResultSetSlice
extends Object
    A Cfaslable slice of a java.sql.ResultSet, used to send SubL portions of a result set.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      ResultSetSlice(ResultSet rs, Integer lo, Integer hi)
      Creates a new ResultSetSlice that contains all rows from lo to hi (both inclusive) from the specified ResultSet.

    • Method Summary

    • Constructor Detail

      • ResultSetSlice

        public ResultSetSlice(ResultSet rs,
              Integer lo,
              Integer hi)
               throws SQLException
        Creates a new ResultSetSlice that contains all rows from lo to hi (both inclusive) from the specified ResultSet. The current row of the underlying ResultSet is set to the row immediately before lo.
        Parameters:
        rs - the ResultSet from which a slice is to be retrieved
        lo - the first row to be retrieved
        hi - the last row to be retrieved
        Throws:
        SQLException - if an SQL error occurs.
